Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第58话\N一切源自桃源乡之夜  后篇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是半妖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要杀要剐就快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半妖的妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该也能当作人面果的养分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜你之赐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让长生不老的果实\N早日腌渍成功
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以快点恢复妖力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管闹  尽管闹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荆棘扎得愈深
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就愈容易吸收到养分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇装四魂碎片的小瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那四魂碎片的主人怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人?我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要装蒜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从戈薇身上抢来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有四魂碎片的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到好消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这房子的某处有女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人也是人面果最喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愈年轻愈好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  我马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前千万别被抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捡到四魂碎片的是这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的箱庭里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇!我这边已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可以开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底想要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点脏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过人面果一定会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是仙人  桃果人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稀奇的半妖与年轻的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时送上门来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子长生不老的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就可以结果了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你遇到了犬夜叉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他出什么事我绝不饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇真的好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能冷静的跟他说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她已经见怪不怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死人了  让你睡一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:07:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我的手都满是泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最痛恨这个没用的人类身体了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  流太多血了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视线模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该还活着吧  半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇的衣服  难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你弄坏了我的葫芦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄取养分变的要花很多功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄取养分?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死胖子  你居然把戈薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你喜欢上了\N那脏兮兮的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上让你们在我的肚子里见面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会变成长生不老的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我吃进肚子里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我饶不了你  死胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些荆棘的根绝对扯不断
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么小的身体能吸到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘在下面的楼层
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股甜甜的气味是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不过是擦伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然变得破破烂烂的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是人类的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还这么逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我们也在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不让你们逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉被扁得好惨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量不要移动比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像能出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走得动吗  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面…还没白天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是一片黑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你还想打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在妖力恢复之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非逃跑不可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到天亮之前  由我保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跳下去果然太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师与七宝\N也必须要先恢复原来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都还没说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算叫我一个人先逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是从箱庭里逃出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷爷您是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来真丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经是桃果人的师父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说  老爷爷也是仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭老头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么\N让那死胖子修炼成仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让那家伙变成仙人的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人面果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人面果?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一个月前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天光是修行  真不想再继续了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有马上变成仙人的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是食物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是人面果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想得到仙人的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就吃下我人面果的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快  吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能和我一同修得仙术了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  连籽也吞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能得到仙人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一吃下人面果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心智就会受人面果支配
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是桃果人仿佛被命令般
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了结出长生不老的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我做成人面果的肥料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您现在的样子是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了长生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有果实是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须把果实熬成长生不老药
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而知道方法的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才让你用这样子活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有本事逃到这地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片的威力增强了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃果人已经不是人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你们收拾掉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我已经不是人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类不就是脏兮兮的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后年纪大了等死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸老妈就是这样死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不想要\N这种脆弱的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这根本就不是强悍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牺牲别人只为了自己\N长命百岁的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不是坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.91,0:13:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆  我很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强的人就能利用脆弱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连这一点都不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人面果给予脆弱的我强悍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使我成为最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我一定能永远活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脆弱的家伙就当肥料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你不能乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对这家伙讲道理是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最了解人类身体的脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与想要变强的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我看到你就觉得恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在对我说教吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连站都站不起来的软脚虾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这死胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有资格说我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这怪物融入四魂碎片之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人面果的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他喝一口这种药
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是桃果人制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长生不老之秘药的赝品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对治疗伤口立刻就能见效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是喝下它之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会受人面果的控制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会  不要吃果实就没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  想得救的话就喝下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝就喝没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多点精神打起来才好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人面果是拿人类当肥料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要喝这种会让人恶心的药
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把我和你混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半妖  你不喝下这种药的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不喝这种鬼东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有嘴巴厉害而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的身体根本没希望嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我现在的身体\N施展风穴大概也无效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弓箭是杀不死桃果人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以打倒他的  绝对!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从弓箭散发破魔之气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位姑娘…到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃果人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,败战武士的弓会有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你一定要除掉桃果人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样勉强能让我赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成弓箭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙人老爷爷用尽最后的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你大卸八块
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使透过背后也能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是四魂碎片的光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要贯穿那道光的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片被…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快趴下  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种人类的身体  你也会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  只要戈薇还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人面果  你是来救我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不想让重要的肥料溜掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能自由行动的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还得到这么多四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来我就是最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也和我合为一体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  天总算亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要连半妖的身体也弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后我就能为所欲为了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别作梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧  桃果人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  妖树人面果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少胡说八道  半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招  风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是桃果人的死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让妖术解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,箱庭里的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在应该也恢复原貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃果人死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉掉下去时天色还很暗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朔日还没有天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可能…就那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉死掉了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.53,0:21:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他已经受了那么重的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是以人类的身体\N从这种峭壁坠落的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会有救
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起供养他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉也算达成心愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.25,0:22:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他\N不惜舍命也救了戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了救我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这种方式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.32,0:22:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点都不觉得高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他明明没有妖力\N还这么勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大笨蛋犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋  犬夜叉是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了不就什么都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后要怎么办啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错!犬夜叉是大笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放着你们不管\N就在那里胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.85,0:22:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得你应该不会那么轻易就死的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:22:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪会那么容易就挂掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要做无谓的担心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫做无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.14,0:23:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担心你是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就知道你会奋不顾身了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正没事不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.11,0:23:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明在哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.62,0:23:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哭了\N没有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哭了\N没有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哭了\N吵死了  坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真的挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:49.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:24:01.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:08.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:17.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:24.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.67,0:24:31.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.15,0:24:38.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.62,0:24:46.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.03,0:24:54.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.99,0:25:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.22,0:25:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不在的这几天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.12,0:25:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人感觉度日如年
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.63,0:25:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.23,0:25:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在驱魔师的村子\N有人想成为你的徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.20,0:25:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们说希望你传授\N驱除妖怪的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.00,0:25:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是一对美少女姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.63,0:25:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人羡慕…不  似乎很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.64,0:25:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.97,0:25:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美少女姐妹花拜师学艺
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.48,0:25:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.91,0:25:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛!
